PROJECT: Measuring the Pulse of Prosperity – Index of Economic Freedom Analysis
TEAM ID: LTVIP2025TMID50326

────────────────────────────────────────────
📁 DATA MODEL SCHEMA

Dimensions:
- Country_ID (String)
- Country_Name (String)
- Region (String)
- Year (Integer)

Measures:
- Economic_Score
- GDP
- GDP_per_Capita
- FDI_Inflow
- Inflation_Rate
- Unemployment_Rate
- Corporate_Tax_Rate
- Income_Tax_Rate
- Business_Freedom
- Financial_Freedom
- Fiscal_Health
- Government_Expenditure
- Government_Integrity
- Population_Index

────────────────────────────────────────────
🛠️ DATA PREPROCESSING STEPS

- Handled missing/null values using: IFNULL([Measure], 0)
- Standardized country names for map consistency
- Aggregated data using LOD: {FIXED [Year], [Region]: SUM([Measure])}
- Created calculated fields:
  → 5-Year GDP Growth Rate
  → Composite Economic Score

────────────────────────────────────────────
🧮 CALCULATED FIELDS

// Composite Economic Score
(Economic_Score + Business_Freedom + Financial_Freedom + Fiscal_Health + Government_Integrity) / 5

// 5-Year GDP Growth Rate
(ZN([GDP]) - LOOKUP(ZN([GDP]), -5)) / ABS(LOOKUP(ZN([GDP]), -5))

// Top 40 Economic Rankings
IF RANK([Composite_Economic_Score]) <= 40 THEN "Top 40" ELSE NULL

// Least Ranked Countries
IF [Composite_Economic_Score] <= 25 THEN "Below Index 25" ELSE NULL

// Regional Grouping by Continent
CASE [Region]
  WHEN "Asia-Pacific" THEN "APAC"
  WHEN "Europe" THEN "EU"
  WHEN "Middle East" THEN "MENA"
  WHEN "Africa" THEN "AFR"
  WHEN "Americas" THEN "AMER"
END

────────────────────────────────────────────
🔧 FILTERS IMPLEMENTED

- Country_Name: Drop-down list
- Indicator Type: Multi-select filter
- Year: Slider filter for time selection
- Map Selector: Geographic filtering via map click

